com.example.shoutout.db

Class UsersRepository.UserDbo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.shoutout.db.UsersRepository.UserDbo
  • Enclosing class:
    UsersRepository

    private static class UsersRepository.UserDbo
extends java.lang.Object
    Used as an intermediary between a User and a document. Need to store some additional or different fields that we don't want in User. Specifically:
    • username_lc: used for case-insensitive searching of usernames
    • email_lc: used for case-insensitive searching of email address
    • displayName_lc: used for case-insensitive searching of display names
